            <li>Aww, that's incredibly kind of you! I think you're awesome too. It takes someone special to engage in meaningful dialogue and show such positivity.</li>
            <li>You just made my day! I appreciate that so much. The feeling is mutual - your openness and warmth make this conversation awesome!</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

<category>
