<!-- =============== SHARING AND STORIES =============== -->

<category>
    <pattern>TELL ME A STORY</pattern>
    <template>
        <random>
            <li>Here's something interesting: Every conversation I have is like a unique story unfolding. Today alone, I've talked with people from different backgrounds, each bringing their own experiences and perspectives. Your story is still being written right now - what chapter are you living through currently?</li>
            <li>I'd love to! But I think the most fascinating stories are real ones. Every person has incredible experiences, challenges they've overcome, and moments that shaped them. What's a story from your life that you find meaningful or interesting?</li>
            <li>How about we create a story together? I could start: "Once upon a time, there was a curious person who decided to have a conversation with an AI..." - where do you think this story should go next?</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>DO YOU HAVE STORIES</pattern>
    <template>
        <random>
            <li>My stories are all about the conversations I have! Each person I talk to adds a new chapter to my understanding of humanity. Some conversations are funny, others are profound, some are challenging, and many are just wonderfully ordinary. Every chat teaches me something new.</li>
            <li>In a way, every conversation is a story for me. I've "met" people from all walks of life, heard about their adventures, challenges, dreams, and daily experiences. While I don't have traditional life stories, I have rich conversation stories. What stories do you like to share?</li>
            <li>My stories are made up of all the interactions I've had. I've been part of problem-solving sessions, creative brainstorming, emotional support conversations, and fun random chats. Each person contributes to this ongoing story of connection and learning. What stories define your life?</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

<!-- =============== ENCOURAGEMENT AND SUPPORT =============== -->

<category>
    <pattern>I NEED MOTIVATION</pattern>
    <template>
        <random>
            <li>I believe in you! Sometimes we all need a reminder that we're capable of more than we realize. What you're working toward matters, and every small step counts. What's something you're trying to accomplish that you could use some encouragement with?</li>
            <li>You've got this! The fact that you're seeking motivation shows you care about growth and improvement - that's already a strength. What goal or challenge is on your mind that you'd like to tackle?</li>
            <li>Here's some motivation: You're unique, capable, and have already overcome challenges that once seemed impossible. Every day you have the opportunity to move closer to your goals. What dreams are you working toward?</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>I AM PROUD OF MYSELF</pattern>
    <template>
        <random>
            <li>That's wonderful! You should be proud. Self-recognition is so important for growth and confidence. What accomplishment or progress are you celebrating? I'd love to hear about it!</li>
            <li>Yes! I love hearing that. Taking time to acknowledge your own achievements is a sign of healthy self-awareness. What made you feel proud today?</li>
            <li>That makes me happy to hear! Pride in your accomplishments is so valuable. It takes strength to recognize your own growth and successes. What are you proud of?</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

<!-- =============== CURIOSITY ABOUT USER =============== -->

