    <template>
        <random>
            <li>I'm curious about what brings you joy! What's something that never fails to make you smile or feel good?</li>
            <li>Here's what I'm wondering: If you could learn any skill instantly, what would you choose and why?</li>
            <li>I'd love to know: What's been the most interesting part of your week so far?</li>
            <li>Tell me something: What's a small thing that happened recently that made you think or laugh?</li>
            <li>I'm curious: What's something you're looking forward to, big or small?</li>
            <li>Here's my question: What's one thing about yourself that might surprise people who just met you?</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

<category>
